{"tid":480216,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"全力支持伊斯蘭教攻佔全世界","createTime":"2017-11-26T02:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T14:51:50.000Z","uid":47356,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cce659ac57b89a554474069d6dd5af1ac5f0e223","tid":480216,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:20:17.000Z","msg":"反正會仆街既都係班臭閪<br />\n<br />\n可蘭經部分章節說明：<br />\n1. 第2章第223節：「你的女人就像你的農田一樣，你可以隨時耕種。」意味丈夫可隨時與妻子發生性行為，毋須理會她的意願<br />\n2. 第4章第34節：「男人的權力壓到女性，因為真主令男人的地位比女人高一等，而且男人花自己的財富去供養她們。」<br />\n3. 第4章第34節：「若擔心妻子不服從，就要適當提醒她(以真主的教誨)，在床時冷落她甚至打她。不過若妻子表現服從，你就無權這樣做。」<br />\n4. 第23章第5-6節：「信徒應該堅守自己的私處...不過與妻子，以及那些被合法佔有的女奴發生性行為則不受此限。」<br />\n5. 第4章第3節：「你可以娶兩、三甚至四個女人，但如果你不能公平地對待她們，你就應該只娶一個，或者娶你的女奴。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20130921/51746047\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20130921%2F51746047&d=r%2F49uCi42EMBuif2e4VsKPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=5dc3c1cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20130921%2F51746047&h=ec0396f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20130921/51746047</a><br />\n<br />\n定時捐錢比伊朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a566c62e321b10914c6cf80acc9866c2e0b24d1","tid":480216,"uid":3558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:20:57.000Z","msg":"On99"},{"pid":"bb07753ecc86202f71be13a24202d424d654414b","tid":480216,"uid":47356,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On99</blockquote><br />\n臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c533496bf9fe08e5a7ab493254cf8044fc61ad33","tid":480216,"uid":37869,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:33:36.000Z","msg":"如果