6,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/婦女與伊斯蘭教\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E5%A9%A6%E5%A5%B3%E8%88%87%E4%BC%8A%E6%96%AF%E8%98%AD%E6%95%99&d=r%2F49uCi42EMBuif2e4VsKPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=c8a443ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/婦女與伊斯蘭教</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n妻子如果因為拒絕與丈夫行房而引致他憤怒地入睡，她會被天神（天使）詛咒直至早晨。（4:54:460）"},{"pid":"c8b329753b7794a4874a3f394da32fcee49a605d","tid":480216,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:09:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/伊斯蘭婚姻法學\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E4%BC%8A%E6%96%AF%E8%98%AD%E5%A9%9A%E5%A7%BB%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%B8&d=r%2F49uCi42EMBuif2e4VsKPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=60ed4c8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/伊斯蘭婚姻法學</a><br />\n<br />\n根據伊斯蘭教法，婚姻是一男一女之間的一種法律關係及社會契約。<strong>在伊斯蘭教裏，婚姻雖然並非強制性，</strong>不過，<strong>結婚是聖行的一種，所以伊斯蘭教強烈建議穆斯林成婚，而不鼓勵獨身</strong>。古蘭經及先知都沒有明確指定適婚年齡，各個社群可以依情況自行決定。在符合一些條件下，一夫多妻制是允許的，但嚴禁一妻多夫制。"},{"pid":"548e4a942e264f11e65287e642bdf864c917a029","tid":480216,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b610a7ecf4d001e74721b47922573d6008216f","tid":480216,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:40:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be800836ce5c32f9021e28bcfed725a65968ac2a","tid":480216,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T02:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾宗教<br />\n阿拉伯帝國真係好撚狗閪</blockquote><br />\n當年波斯帝國竟然會輸俾呢D沒文化/沒文字的生蕃..."},{"pid":"e3991d87fc94c581b94ec2b5b9e865e17ef05e60","tid":480216,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"